      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know, it feels different than just \"imperfections\". like, if a species is just broken or can't adapt, doesn't nature just... prune it? tell me the truth, from a strictly biological standpoint, what happens to things that dont fit? do they actually have a place in the system?",
